1
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:25,980
(Mingguang Temple)

2
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:07,420
Prefect Sun Mao?

3
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:19,100
=The Tang Mist S1=

4
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:39,740
=Episode 22=

5
00:02:44,111 --> 00:02:45,710
There are burn marks on his hands.

6
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,080
A long wound on the back of his head.

7
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:50,430
Likely caused by the edge
of a blunt object.

8
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:53,780
The fatal injury matches
the previous three female victims.

9
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:55,910
His neck was snapped by force.

10
00:02:56,133 --> 00:02:57,240
His tongue wasn't cut out.

11
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,750
Judging by the state of the body,

12
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,240
he died around twelve hours ago.

13
00:03:01,311 --> 00:03:02,777
Around late Xu hour last night.

14
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:04,870
Magistrate Wu.

15
00:03:05,844 --> 00:03:07,511
What connection did Prefect Sun have

16
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,910
with the three female victims
before his death?

17
00:03:10,177 --> 00:03:11,533
None, as far as I'm concerned.

18
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,120
He only visited to comfort
the victims' families.

19
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,080
Where were all of you

20
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,470
around late Xu hour last night?

21
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,960
Did you hear

22
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,960
or see anything?

23
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,240
Oh, merciful Buddha.

24
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,840
My Dharma name is Huiwu.

25
00:03:33,933 --> 00:03:35,177
I'm the abbot of the temple.

26
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,680
Last night was my late master's
memorial day.

27
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:40,240
I was chanting in the hall
with all the monks.

28
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,360
And with the thunder
raging through the night,

29
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,000
I didn't realize

30
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,430
when Prefect Sun

31
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:47,310
entered the temple.

32
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,911
None of you heard anything either?

33
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,750
Why would the murderer

34
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,750
hide the body

35
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,710
inside the incense burner?

36
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,390
There are scuff marks

37
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,000
on the back heel of the shoes.

38
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,190
What's this place?

39
00:04:41,688 --> 00:04:43,800
(Clear the Mind, Purify the Heart)
Why is it locked?

40
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,040
Sir,

41
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,390
this is the Repentance Room.

42
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:47,750
It's a place for remorse.

43
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,190
Everyone is burdened

44
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:51,560
by their sins and mistakes.

45
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,920
They come here to repent
and reflect upon themselves.

46
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,070
Jueyi,

47
00:05:08,266 --> 00:05:09,240
you may step outside.

48
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:27,920
Who is he?

49
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,680
He used to be a merchant
from Xin'an County named Jia Zhishan.

50
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,750
Something seemed
to weigh on his conscience,

51
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,430
and he became haunted by nightmares.

52
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,830
To cleanse himself of sin,

53
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,720
he donated his fortune to the temple

54
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,750
and practiced here as a lay disciple.

55
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:42,600
This Repentance Room
has saved more than ten people...

56
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,390
Wujue,

57
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,133
do not speak carelessly.

58
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,240
Understood, Abbot.

59
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,750
This way, please.

60
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,870
These are all prayer tokens.

61
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,630
Each of them carries

62
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,720
the sincere wishes of the worshipers.

63
00:06:16,730 --> 00:06:17,950
Oh, merciful Buddha.

64
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:20,600
May Buddha show blessings.

65
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,800
Oh, merciful Buddha.

66
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,720
(Looks like)

67
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,190
(this is the real crime scene.)

68
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:39,120
The murderer hid Sun Mao
inside the incense burner

69
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,800
to conceal

70
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:42,880
the incense ash left on him
from this place.

71
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:44,750
Magistrate Wu,

72
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,480
investigate everyone

73
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,310
who entered the Repentance Room
yesterday.

74
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,390
Yes, sir.

75
00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:53,540
(Sun Mao's Study)

76
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:56,800
Why is the prefect's residence
so impoverished?

77
00:07:56,888 --> 00:07:59,177
(Butler of the Prefect's Residence)
Prefect Sun didn't like extravagance.

78
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,450
He devoted himself to the people

79
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,844
and spent all his family's fortune

80
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,960
helping them.

81
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,720
He was a good man.

82
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:08,390
He spent most of his time in this study.

83
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:09,360
How could

84
00:08:09,690 --> 00:08:10,720
someone like him

85
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,430
meet such a terrible end?

86
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:16,870
Madam.

87
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,040
I, Wu,

88
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,720
greet you, Commissioner Di.

89
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,750
There's no need for formalities.

90
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,870
Why did Prefect Sun

91
00:08:27,870 --> 00:08:29,311
go to Mingguang Temple last night?

92
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,630
I don't know.

93
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,240
Yesterday, the magistrate came

94
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:35,120
to report a murder case,

95
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,200
and he hurried out soon after.

96
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:38,510
And...

97
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,550
he never returned.

98
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:42,630
Had he shown

99
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,510
any unusual behavior lately?

100
00:08:55,830 --> 00:08:56,870
Madam,

101
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,630
do you recognize
the women in these portraits?

102
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,030
This is Yanzhi.

103
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,910
These are the other victims.

104
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,480
Did they have something to do
with my husband's death?

105
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,720
I came

106
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,000
because I wish to know

107
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,390
what relationship the Prefect had

108
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:16,240
with these women while he was alive.

109
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,711
My husband would never fool around

110
00:09:17,733 --> 00:09:19,270
with other women.

111
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,790
Sister, there's no need
to waste words with them.

112
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:23,670
You know what kind of man

113
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,750
my brother-in-law was.

114
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,720
He cared about the people.

115
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,320
He even paid for the burials

116
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,550
to comfort

117
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,910
the victims' families.

118
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:34,910
I will not tolerate anyone
who tries to slander him.

119
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:36,720
Zidi.

120
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:44,020
(Xin'an County Bureau)

121
00:09:46,630 --> 00:09:48,320
The case is still unsolved,

122
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,630
yet he paid for the burials
out of his own pocket.

123
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,630
Prefect Sun specially approved

124
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:53,510
my daughter's burial

125
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,750
so she could rest in peace.

126
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:56,870
Specially approved?

127
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,750
Was it kindness,

128
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,320
or an attempt
to silence public discussion?

129
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,030
What

130
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:05,630
is hidden here?

131
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,440
Sir, look.

132
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,780
This black residue isn't ash.

133
00:10:15,688 --> 00:10:17,440
Every brush, inkstone, paper,
and inkstick

134
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:18,870
in Sun Mao's study

135
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,230
was covered in thick dust.

136
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,270
There was no ink
inside the Repentance Room either,

137
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,670
nor anything else

138
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,390
that could leave black marks.

139
00:10:26,555 --> 00:10:28,666
Could it have been left behind
by the murderer?

140
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:34,010
Sir, this is the register of everyone

141
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,444
who entered the Repentance Room.

142
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,000
Just as Huiwu said,

143
00:10:37,444 --> 00:10:38,480
all worshippers had left

144
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,200
by early Xu hour.

145
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,200
Nothing unusual was noticed.

146
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:45,300
(Bai Zhi entered to offer around late
You hour and left at early Xu hour.)

147
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,150
Bai Zhi.

148
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:48,960
Beauty in Red.

149
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,120
Officer,

150
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,480
over here.

151
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,150
Come on.

152
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:56,360
(Xin'an County Bureau)

153
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,480
Officer.

154
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,440
What brings you here,

155
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,440
Lady Chunhua?

156
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,390
Officer,

157
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,240
I heard

158
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,670
the magistrate
is investigating Mingguang Temple.

159
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:05,720
I have information.

160
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,120
But let me make this clear.

161
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,240
I'm not someone who spreads gossip.

162
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,630
I'm telling only you.

163
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,720
There's no way
you're that kind of person.

164
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:15,440
Go on.

165
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:16,750
Usually,

166
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,720
all worshippers leave by early Xu hour.

167
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,750
But there's one person

168
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:21,750
who goes at early Xu hour

169
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:24,080
and returns around late Xu hour
every single day.

170
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,080
Who?

171
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,240
Bai Zhi.

172
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,600
Bai Zhi again?

173
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,750
You're not jealous

174
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,850
because Lady Bai Zhi is prettier
than you, are you?

175
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:35,480
(Xin'an County Bureau)
How could you say that?

176
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,510
I rushed over
the moment I heard the news,

177
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,550
and this is how you repay my kindness?

178
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,510
Forget it then.

179
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,630
Lady Chunhua...

180
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:48,750
Di.

181
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,670
Bai Zhi is suspicious.

182
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,000
She left around early Xu hour.

183
00:11:55,111 --> 00:11:56,270
What's suspicious about her?

184
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:58,200
She went to Mingguang Temple
last night.

185
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,670
Normally,

186
00:11:58,670 --> 00:12:00,510
she leaves around late Xu hour.

187
00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:02,320
But she left early last night.

188
00:12:30,111 --> 00:12:31,440
Please pardon my humble home.

189
00:12:31,555 --> 00:12:33,266
I only have some plain tea to offer.

190
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:37,960
Lady Bai,

191
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,750
did you go to Mingguang Temple
last night?

192
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,480
Yes.

193
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,360
I went there

194
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,120
to pray for Madam He's health.

195
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,750
What time did you arrive,
and what time did you leave?

196
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:51,440
I usually go

197
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,600
around early Xu hour

198
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,866
and return near late Xu hour.

199
00:12:54,288 --> 00:12:55,910
But last night, I wasn't feeling well,

200
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,390
so I came back soon after I arrived.

201
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,720
You were unwell?

202
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,840
It's an old ailment.

203
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,390
I know a little medicine.

204
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:03,840
Perhaps I can help.

205
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,440
Please sit.

206
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,240
Open your mouth.

207
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,240
Your complexion

208
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,270
and tongue are pale.

209
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,750
Your body is extremely weak.

210
00:13:27,866 --> 00:13:29,933
I'll prepare a prescription
for you later.

211
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,390
Thank you.

212
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,360
Did you see Prefect Sun

213
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:39,440
at Mingguang Temple last night?

214
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,030
No, I didn't.

215
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,960
I heard Wang Zhong
once served as a general.

216
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,480
Why isn't he here?

217
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:49,720
My husband went to work
at my godfather's shop.

218
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:51,320
Two years ago,

219
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,840
he was badly wounded
while saving his commander.

220
00:13:54,466 --> 00:13:55,933
His legs have never fully recovered.

221
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:57,120
These days,

222
00:13:57,622 --> 00:13:59,480
only my godfather is willing
to employ him.

223
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,120
I know some medicine.

224
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,200
Perhaps I could treat him.

225
00:14:02,466 --> 00:14:04,088
There's no need to trouble yourself.

226
00:14:04,266 --> 00:14:06,888
The injury left permanent damage.
It can't be cured.

227
00:14:12,022 --> 00:14:13,960
Bai Zhi does suffer
from a deficiency condition.

228
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:20,630
Here.

229
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,270
Look at this.

230
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,320
Di,

231
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,720
I noticed that too.

232
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:38,300
(Hu Tarvern)

233
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:43,700
(Hu Tarvern)

234
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:50,630
Welcome.

235
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,080
Shopkeeper,

236
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,840
is this road

237
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:57,600
the only route to Mingguang Temple?

238
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:58,640
That's right.

239
00:14:58,650 --> 00:15:00,150
During Xu hour last night,

240
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:02,270
did you see anyone suspicious pass by?

241
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,720
No.

242
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,270
No.

243
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,600
Shopkeeper,

244
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,960
bring us a pot of liquor.

245
00:15:13,630 --> 00:15:13,960
Sir,

246
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,960
what would you like?

247
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:17,870
The kind Lady Bai Zhi usually drinks.

248
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,440
She?

249
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:22,670
Alright.

250
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,120
I'll fetch it.

251
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,270
Please wait a moment.

252
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:29,300
(Hu Tarvern)

253
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:29,960
Ten coins.

254
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:31,790
Does Lady Bai Zhi

255
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,320
drink such cheap liquor?

256
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:36,200
She isn't well-off.

257
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:38,910
Wang Zhong likes to drink,

258
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,320
so she has to pinch every penny.

259
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:43,670
Every time she returns
from Mingguang Temple

260
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,960
and passes my shop,

261
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,550
she buys a bottle.

262
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,270
Did Lady Bai Zhi

263
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:49,670
come to buy liquor yesterday?

264
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,120
No.

265
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,790
I waited for a long time last night,

266
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:55,560
but she never showed up.

267
00:15:55,740 --> 00:15:57,360
Could you have remembered
the time wrong?

268
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,840
Absolutely impossible.

269
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,240
She always heads to

270
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:05,270
Mingguang Temple around early Xu hour

271
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,720
and returns home near late Xu hour.

272
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:10,120
She's followed that routine
without fail.

273
00:16:10,430 --> 00:16:12,510
Last night, I saw her go as usual,

274
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:15,390
but when I closed up at Hai hour,

275
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:16,600
she still hadn't returned.

276
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:18,390
Please enjoy your drink.

277
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:19,790
I'll get back to work.

278
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:22,720
Normally, she leaves
around late Xu hour.

279
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:25,080
But she left early last night.

280
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:28,000
But last night, I wasn't feeling well,
so I came back soon after I arrived.

281
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,550
When I closed up at Hai hour,
she still hadn't returned.

282
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:32,320
(Yanzhi, Lady Gui, Lian)

283
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:35,840
Bai Zhi lied about the time
she left Mingguang Temple.

284
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:39,080
She was definitely still inside
the temple around late Xu hour.

285
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:41,360
The monks patrolled the temple

286
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,750
and found no one remaining.

287
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,360
I didn't realize

288
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:45,870
when Prefect Sun

289
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,630
entered the temple.

290
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,440
Sun Mao's presence

291
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:51,120
went unnoticed.

292
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,270
I don't believe it.

293
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:58,466
Huiwu claimed he saw Bai Zhi
leave the Repentance Room

294
00:16:58,555 --> 00:17:00,440
around early Xu hour.

295
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,080
Why would Huiwu help Bai Zhi
conceal this?

296
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:06,920
(Sun Mao, burn marks...)
It must be connected to Sun Mao's death.

297
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,830
Don't alert them.

298
00:17:08,940 --> 00:17:11,288
Investigate the relationship
between Bai Zhi, Huiwu,

299
00:17:11,333 --> 00:17:12,590
and Sun Mao.

300
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:17,550
Officer.

301
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,110
Back again to dig for gossip?

302
00:17:21,110 --> 00:17:23,750
And what have you heard this time,
four lovely ladies?

303
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:26,030
Oh, we know plenty.

304
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:27,680
What do you want to ask?

305
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:30,960
What's the relationship
between Sun Mao and Bai Zhi?

306
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,440
You mean that kind of relationship?

307
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:33,790
No way.

308
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:34,920
Absolutely impossible.

309
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,640
Prefect Sun was upright and honorable.

310
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,822
He was a good official.

311
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,110
He kept his distance from women.

312
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:40,000
By no means

313
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,720
would he ruin himself over one.

314
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:43,550
That's right. Yanzhi

315
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:45,750
once tried to seduce Prefect Sun,

316
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,200
but he harshly

317
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,640
reprimanded her.

318
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,550
Didn't Prefect Sun

319
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:53,310
once stand up for Bai Zhi
and her husband?

320
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,240
Yes.

321
00:17:54,580 --> 00:17:55,680
That's true.

322
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:56,750
Move!

323
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:57,480
Stop.

324
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,010
Out of the way.

325
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:00,400
What are you doing?

326
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:02,440
Wang Zhong is a general of the Tang.

327
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:04,720
How could he possibly stoop to theft?

328
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,590
You barged into his home

329
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:09,000
without evidence
and smashed the place apart.

330
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,640
Take these men back to the Bureau.

331
00:18:10,870 --> 00:18:11,440
Yes.

332
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:13,000
Please spare us, sir!

333
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,430
We... We'll pay for the damages!

334
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,270
We'll pay!

335
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,510
General Wang,

336
00:18:24,133 --> 00:18:25,466
you've suffered an injustice.

337
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,350
Lady Bai,

338
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,550
I'll punish them severely.

339
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,720
Please accept this

340
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,270
and repair your home.

341
00:18:43,622 --> 00:18:45,333
Thank you for your kindness, sir.

342
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,590
But we can't accept the money.

343
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:55,350
Wang Zhong was crippled in battle

344
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,590
and has no family to rely on.

345
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,310
Bai Zhi supports

346
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:59,240
the whole household herself.

347
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:01,680
Isn't she foolish?

348
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:03,310
It hasn't been easy for her.

349
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,030
Her godfather, He Xun,

350
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,920
is a wealthy merchant in town.

351
00:19:06,930 --> 00:19:08,190
He offered her money,
but she refused it all.

352
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:10,200
Instead, she works as a maid
in the He residence

353
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,920
and serves Madam He.

354
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,510
She only got meager wages.

355
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,110
Exactly.

356
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,030
There's one more thing.

357
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:17,800
Bai Zhi once approached Prefect Sun

358
00:19:17,844 --> 00:19:20,000
about the imperial rewards
owed to Wang Zhong.

359
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,590
Prefect Sun told her
the court had issued no reward.

360
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,133
He even offered to compensate them

361
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,680
out of his own pocket,

362
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:28,440
but Bai Zhi refused that.

363
00:19:28,866 --> 00:19:29,310
Officer.

364
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:30,480
Don't leave yet, officer.

365
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,240
Forget it.

366
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:33,160
Let's go.

367
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,160
Duan, where are you going?

368
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:37,680
The court rewards wounded generals
and soldiers according to merit.

369
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,910
The funds are distributed
through the local prefectures.

370
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,550
Wang Zhong once saved
the commander of an army.

371
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:41,670
His reward should've been considerable.

372
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:44,000
There's no way Sun Mao
wouldn't have known about it.

373
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:44,880
Where are we going?

374
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,044
To the prefectural bureau.

375
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:51,750
Five years ago,

376
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:54,590
Princess Anning
visited Mingguang Temple.

377
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:57,510
She left after the rites ended.

378
00:19:57,960 --> 00:20:01,030
A fire broke out at the temple
that very night.

379
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,030
It was because

380
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:04,790
a monk accidentally knocked over
a candle from the offering table.

381
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:07,550
The flames caught the drapes.

382
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:08,270
Yes.

383
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:10,240
Because of that fire,

384
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,680
all the offerings from Princess Anning
were destroyed.

385
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:14,920
Only a single golden Buddha statue

386
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:15,920
survived the fire.

387
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:18,160
Abbot Yuanzhi

388
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,200
and several monks

389
00:20:19,430 --> 00:20:20,350
perished in the fire

390
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,640
as well.

391
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:24,510
At the time, Huiwu had entered
Mingguang Temple

392
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:25,590
only six years earlier.

393
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,240
Despite his low seniority,

394
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:30,550
he suddenly became abbot
overseeing the entire temple.

395
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,000
Sir,

396
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:35,200
Sun Mao was also promoted to Prefect
five years ago.

397
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:38,160
The promotion was only a few days apart.

398
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,310
That was too much

399
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,030
of a coincidence.

400
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,160
That fire

401
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:46,880
was more than just an accident.

402
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,030
Sun Mao.

403
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,590
Why is a prefect's residence

404
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,880
so impoverished?

405
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:57,310
Prefect Sun didn't like extravagance.

406
00:20:57,355 --> 00:20:58,733
He devoted himself to the people

407
00:20:58,790 --> 00:21:02,640
and spent all his family's fortune
helping them.

408
00:21:03,450 --> 00:21:05,360
Sun Mao's poverty itself

409
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:06,790
is unusual.

410
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:08,200
It raises questions.

411
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:09,510
The butler said...

412
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:12,110
He spent most of his time in this study.

413
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,160
But the brushes,
inkstones, paper, and ink

414
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:16,200
are all coated in thick dust,

415
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,110
as if untouched for a very long time.

416
00:21:19,070 --> 00:21:22,440
What exactly did Sun Mao do
in the study?

417
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:23,750
What secret

418
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:26,720
is hidden here?

419
00:21:29,510 --> 00:21:30,830
Wang Zhong...

420
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:31,880
I remember him.

421
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,200
Found it.

422
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,590
Have a look at this, sir.

423
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,622
3,333 square meters of farmland,
one hundred strings of coins,

424
00:21:39,644 --> 00:21:40,830
and some pieces of jewelry.

425
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:43,550
The rewards were claimed long ago.

426
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:45,590
Why is the signature Zhang Liang?

427
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,240
That's the proxy claimant.

428
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:50,270
If the recipient was injured
and unable to come in person,

429
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,990
a relative could collect it
on their behalf.

430
00:21:52,088 --> 00:21:54,070
Why didn't Bai Zhi come herself?

431
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,680
Do you remember

432
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,350
what the proxy claimant looked like?

433
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:02,240
Square face.

434
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:05,400
Small eyes.

435
00:22:06,070 --> 00:22:07,400
Big mouth.

436
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:10,830
His nose looked a bit like
Magistrate Wu's.

437
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,200
His eyebrows

438
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:14,790
were thicker.

439
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:16,000
No beard.

440
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,440
Did he have a mole here?

441
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,400
Yes, he did.

442
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,160
He had a mole.

443
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:24,790
He did.

444
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:28,240
Lad,

445
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:31,640
when describing someone,

446
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:34,270
start with the distinctive features.

447
00:22:42,590 --> 00:22:44,240
Sun Mao's brother-in-law,

448
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,790
Wu Zidi.

449
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:50,180
(Sun Mao's Study)

450
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:12,510
A weiqi board?

451
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,790
Why is there a weiqi board hidden here?

452
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:27,100
The white stones are trapped
in a losing position.

453
00:23:27,950 --> 00:23:30,030
But if one white stone is moved,

454
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:33,270
the entire game can be turned around.

455
00:24:13,140 --> 00:24:14,260
(Preview of Next Episode)

456
00:24:18,350 --> 00:24:19,680
My daughter Shuitao

457
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:20,888
left home around the You hour

458
00:24:20,933 --> 00:24:23,270
and has yet to return, sir!

459
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,830
Abbot Yuanzhi has perished
in the flames.

460
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:35,270
If you wish to join him,

461
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,200
I'll grant your wish.

462
00:24:37,270 --> 00:24:38,310
Which woman?

463
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,640
I told you

464
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:43,070
Wang Zhong wasn't a good man.

465
00:24:47,391 --> 00:24:48,971
♪Night covers the long streets♪

466
00:24:50,051 --> 00:24:51,761
♪The city remains silent♪

467
00:24:53,151 --> 00:24:54,741
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

468
00:24:55,001 --> 00:24:57,241
♪Words still left unspoken♪

469
00:24:58,641 --> 00:25:00,281
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

470
00:25:01,411 --> 00:25:03,881
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

471
00:25:04,501 --> 00:25:05,981
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

472
00:25:05,981 --> 00:25:09,121
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

473
00:25:09,741 --> 00:25:11,661
♪Love is born from desire♪

474
00:25:12,351 --> 00:25:14,481
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

475
00:25:15,621 --> 00:25:17,281
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

476
00:25:17,281 --> 00:25:20,581
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

477
00:25:22,031 --> 00:25:23,351
♪Someone once warned me♪

478
00:25:23,351 --> 00:25:24,871
♪To stop upon this shore♪

479
00:25:24,871 --> 00:25:26,191
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

480
00:25:26,191 --> 00:25:27,681
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

481
00:25:27,681 --> 00:25:28,801
♪If one thought retreats♪

482
00:25:28,801 --> 00:25:30,101
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

483
00:25:30,101 --> 00:25:31,441
♪But in this world♪

484
00:25:31,441 --> 00:25:33,841
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

485
00:25:35,671 --> 00:25:38,481
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

486
00:25:38,481 --> 00:25:39,951
♪Still I walk ahead♪

487
00:25:40,181 --> 00:25:41,401
♪Let it pierce through♪

488
00:25:41,401 --> 00:25:46,141
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

489
00:25:46,141 --> 00:25:48,381
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

490
00:25:48,381 --> 00:25:49,781
♪Covering every heart♪

491
00:25:49,781 --> 00:25:50,971
♪How many people♪

492
00:25:51,231 --> 00:25:52,601
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

493
00:25:52,601 --> 00:25:54,811
♪Yet call it♪

494
00:25:55,011 --> 00:25:56,351
♪Fate?♪

495
00:25:56,711 --> 00:25:57,891
♪Life and death♪

496
00:25:57,891 --> 00:25:59,151
♪Balanced on a single line♪

497
00:25:59,501 --> 00:26:00,671
♪Light and shadow♪

498
00:26:00,671 --> 00:26:01,931
♪Hanging side by side♪

499
00:26:01,931 --> 00:26:03,411
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

500
00:26:03,411 --> 00:26:04,821
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

501
00:26:04,821 --> 00:26:06,361
♪In the end, it is only♪

502
00:26:06,361 --> 00:26:07,741
♪A single misguided thought♪

503
00:26:07,741 --> 00:26:09,301
♪If unveiling the truth♪

504
00:26:09,301 --> 00:26:10,641
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

505
00:26:10,641 --> 00:26:11,811
♪Then this answer♪

506
00:26:11,811 --> 00:26:13,171
♪Can it still remain true?♪

507
00:26:13,171 --> 00:26:14,571
♪When love and law♪

508
00:26:14,571 --> 00:26:16,051
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

509
00:26:16,051 --> 00:26:17,451
♪Which figure before me♪

510
00:26:17,451 --> 00:26:24,651
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

511
00:26:24,651 --> 00:26:27,381
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

512
00:26:27,381 --> 00:26:28,971
♪Still I walk ahead♪

513
00:26:28,971 --> 00:26:30,211
♪Not for fame or glory♪

514
00:26:30,211 --> 00:26:35,081
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

515
00:26:35,081 --> 00:26:36,891
♪Human nature is clouded♪

516
00:26:36,891 --> 00:26:38,611
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

517
00:26:38,611 --> 00:26:40,081
♪Though this world♪

518
00:26:40,081 --> 00:26:41,451
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

519
00:26:41,451 --> 00:26:43,701
♪There is still a light♪

520
00:26:43,701 --> 00:26:46,661
♪Worth pursuing♪

521
00:26:46,661 --> 00:26:48,481
♪Every case has its ending♪

522
00:26:48,481 --> 00:26:49,741
♪But night does not always fade♪

523
00:26:50,011 --> 00:26:51,391
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

524
00:26:51,391 --> 00:26:52,611
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

525
00:26:52,881 --> 00:26:53,961
♪If justice stands♪

526
00:26:53,961 --> 00:26:55,211
♪Without mercy beside it♪

527
00:26:55,211 --> 00:26:57,011
♪Then how is it♪

528
00:26:57,011 --> 00:27:06,571
♪Any different from a blade?♪

529
00:27:06,571 --> 00:27:09,761
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

530
00:27:09,761 --> 00:27:11,241
♪Still I walk ahead♪

531
00:27:11,241 --> 00:27:12,631
♪Even if the world♪

532
00:27:12,631 --> 00:27:17,361
♪Refuses to answer♪

533
00:27:17,361 --> 00:27:19,321
♪When every hidden truth♪

534
00:27:19,321 --> 00:27:21,031
♪Finally reveals itself♪

535
00:27:21,031 --> 00:27:22,391
♪I only wish♪

536
00:27:22,391 --> 00:27:23,871
♪To hold on♪

537
00:27:23,871 --> 00:27:28,611
♪Within the darkness♪

538
00:27:28,611 --> 00:27:30,611
♪To the heart♪
